song_lyrics: Dhanya dhanya chhe Āṇand gām ne dhanya Charotar desh,
Pragaṭ thayā chhe Swāmī Jabalpur gāmmā,
Vinod vādhyo apār, pragaṭyā Mahant Swāmī... 1
Shāstrījī Mahārāje āshiṣh arpyā, pitā Maṇibhāī sāmbhaḷīne harakhyā,
Karashe moṭā moṭā kām, pragaṭyā Mahant Swāmī... 2
Yogījīno e sankalp baḷiyo, sādhu ekāvan karavāno zīliyo,
Pahel kīdhī chhe ā vār, pragaṭyā Mahant Swāmī... 3
Yogījīne khūb rājī kīdhā’tā, Pramukh Swāmīnā paḍachhāyā thyā’tā,
Haiye Hari dhāranār, pragaṭyā Mahant Swāmī... 4
Pramukh Swāmīnu swarūp āp chho, sādhutānā shaṇagāre shobho chho,
title: Dhanya dhanya chhe Āṇand gām ne dhanya Charotar desh
